HEADWORD: Postclavicle
<hw>Post*clav"i*cle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>clavicle</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>A
bone in the pectoral girdle of many fishes projecting backward from the
clavicle.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Post`*cla*vic"u*lar</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
